<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/55058833" target="_blank" data-id="14243568" data-za-element-name="Title">
请问学习前端最有效的办法是什么？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/55058833/answer/142434915">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="52503312">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="142434915"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>261</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">261</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label sr-only">反对</span>
