<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20140718" target="_blank" data-id="236351" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何写一个类似 LESS 的编译工具？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20140718/answer/114360444">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="41224201">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="114360444"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>258</a>
