<a data-follow="q:link" class="follow-link zg-follow meta-item" href="javascript:;" id="sfb-7803164"><i class="z-icon-follow"></i>关注问题</a>

<a href="#" name="addcomment" class="meta-item toggle-comment js-toggleCommentBox">
<i class="z-icon-comment"></i>37 条评论</a>


<a href="#" class="meta-item zu-autohide js-thank" data-thanked="false"><i class="z-icon-thank"></i>感谢</a>



