<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/21497720" target="_blank" data-id="779763" data-za-element-name="Title">
关于 AngularJS 框架的使用有哪些经验值得分享？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/21497720/answer/18441053">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="2526668">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="18441053"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>255</a>
