<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/31809713" target="_blank" data-id="4923094" data-za-element-name="Title">
网上都说操作真实 DOM 慢，但测试结果却比 React 更快，为什么？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/31809713/answer/54833728">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="17340227">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="54833728"> -->

