<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$fredriklo"
target="_blank" href="/people/fredriklo"
>罗志宇</a></span><span title="Opera 欧朋 CTO" class="bio">
Opera 欧朋 CTO
